('tt0030063','free','The Divorce of Lady X (1938)','1938','1h 32min','Leslie Steele, a guest at a ball at the Royal Park Hotel, is forced to stay overnight there because of thick London fog.  As no rooms are available, Miss Steele talks her way into sharing a suite with Everard Logan, a handsome though somewhat stiff lawyer. All his efforts to oust her are to no avail and she even ends up talking him out of his pyjamas.
