('tt0049922','free','The Violent Years (1956)','1956','1h 5min','Paula Parkins, the spoiled daughter of a well-to-do newspaper editor father and a socialite mother, gets her kicks by organizing and directing a gang of bored young women like herself. The gang dresses in men''s attire, robs gas stations, and terrorizes habitués of a local lovers'' lane—even raping a young gentleman (off camera) after tying up his girlfriend.
