('tt0057012','free','Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb (1964)','1964','1h 35min','United States Air Force Brigadier General Jack D. Ripper is commander of Burpelson Air Force Base, which houses the Strategic Air Command (SAC) 843rd Bomb Wing, flying B-52 bombers armed with hydrogen bombs. The 843rd Wing is flying on airborne alert, two hours from their targets inside the USSR.

