('tt0043397','free','Chained for Life (1952)','1952','1h 21min','The movie opens with a judge (Norval Mitchell) begging the audience for help in resolving a terrible dilemma. The action moves to a courtroom, where Vivian Hamilton is on trial for the shooting death of her sister''s lover. The story unfolds in flashback as various characters are called to testify.
