('tt0006206','free','Les vampires (1915)','1915','7h 1min','Lensed in an eerily abandoned Paris in 1915, Louis Feuillade''s stark chapterplay LES VAMPIRES is a grim and powerful work which is worlds apart from the later glitz and polish of the golden age serials produced by the American studios.

