('tt0029606','free','A Star Is Born (1937)','1937','1h 51min','North Dakota farm girl Esther Victoria Blodgett yearns to become a Hollywood actress.  Although her aunt and father discourage such thoughts, Esther''s grandmother gives Esther her savings to follow her dream.
