('tt0006864','free','Intolerance: Love''s Struggle Throughout the Ages (1916)','1916','2h 43min','The film consists of four distinct, but parallel, stories—intercut with increasing frequency as the film builds to a climax—that demonstrate humankind''s persistent intolerance throughout the ages. The timeline covers approximately 2,500 years.

